Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:05.16,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改變些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.88,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要個契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:10.55,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飛奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:14.72,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回憶在騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:20.31,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像認識你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:24.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不論是晴天雨天還是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.19,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我都好想好想去見你
